==German==

===Etymology===
Cognates: Dutch [[-zaam]].

===Suffix===
'''-sam'''
# Used to form an [[adjective]] or an [[adverb]], depending on the context.
#: ''[[lang]]'' ("lengthy in duration") + '''''-sam''''': ''[[langsam]]'' ("[[slow]]", "[[slowly]]")
#: ''[[aufmerken]]'' ("to [[observe]]")+ '''''-sam''''': ''[[aufmerksam]]'' ("[[observant]]", "[[attentively]]")

